The match 3 game I have been waiting for! Has some great little puzzles, you are working towards building wonders which is a great incentive. And best of all NO AD'S NO WAITING TO UNLOCK LIVES just play when you want to play. I don't know why this is so hard to find these days but kudos to the developers. My only gripe is power's. I want a straight up challenging game that is based entirely on skill but so far I just don't use them and it has been a good challenge. Thank you!  Edit- I'm knocking this review back to a 4 stars because despite me purchasing for the full game and it having no online functionality I am currently travelling around Asia without data and what do you know it won't allow me to start the game offline. ANNOYING üò°

content: I really enjoyed playing this. It had nice game play and really cool sound effects. The power-ups were painless to charge and very helpful. I found all the wonders to be very visually appealing, especially the ones with water. Oh and it has 4 game modes, insane, difficult, normal and zen. I played on Zen. If you like match 3 games, you should TOTALLY play this.

Finally! A game on the App Store that doesn't try to cheat us with In App Purchases! 7 Wonders is a beautiful game with addicitng gameplay that goes at your own pace, not at the pace of a freemium game. After playing so much freemium, I lost the idea that I could actually play a game without having to pay for anything besides the game itself. Seriously, thanks Mumbo Jumbo for putting out a premium and beautiful game! I am on Shangri La and loving it! I also love the mini objectives in each level as well! Tons of replay value! Thank you!

This company has been making commercial games for PCs for years and years. I have been playing 7 wonders on the PC for years and it's one of my favorites. I was curious what they would do with the Android version and I was not disappointed. The graphics are great, the gameplay is addictive, and they even added side games. There are different achievements to challenge you, different styles and levels of play, and even a super bonus level if you get a high enough score. It's just a great game!
